'''Bruno Fait''' (born 7 July 1924) is an [[Italy|Italian]] former [[Racewalking|racewalker]] who competed in the [[1952 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=sref>{{cite web|title=Olympics |url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/fa/bruno-fait-1.html|publisher=sports-reference|accessdate=6 July 2012}}</ref>

==Biography==
After his sport career he emigrated in [[France]] and became a writer.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://trentinocorrierealpi.gelocal.it/cronaca/2011/09/03/news/fait-in-libreria-con-un-nuovo-romanzo-1.4007965|title=Fait in libreria con un nuovo romanzo|publisher=trentinocorrierealpi.gelocal.it|language=italian|accessdate=1 December 2012}}</ref>

